OL,6,FThe mother of a young girl who was
OL,7,Flocked in a toilet by a dance teacher
OL,8,Fto protect her from the Southport
OL,9,Fattacker says she initially believed
OL,10,Fher daughter had died.
OL,12,FIn an impact statement, the mother of
OL,13,Fthe girl, known as Child X for legal
OL,14,Freasons, told the public inquiry into
OL,15,Fthe events she could not find her
OL,16,Fdaughter anywhere in the "chaos"
OL,17,Ffollowing the attack.
OL,19,FShe said it quickly became clear her
OL,20,Fdaughter was inside the building "with
OL,21,Fhim".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
