OL,3,CMother thought daughter had died in
OL,4,CSouthport attack
OL,6,F"Time stopped and everything seemed to
OL,7,Fmove in slow motion," she said.
OL,9,FThe mum told the inquiry she followed
OL,10,Fpolice into the building, but was
OL,11,Fstopped from entering the room, and
OL,12,Fleft "believing that my daughter had
OL,13,Fdied".
OL,15,F"I called my parents hysterically
OL,16,Ftelling them that she was dead," she
OL,17,Ftold the inquiry. "I cannot begin to
OL,18,Fimagine what that moment did to them
OL,19,Fand I know they relive this frequently.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
