OL,3,CMother thought daughter had died in
OL,4,CSouthport attack
OL,6,F"But then, in the middle of the
OL,7,Fnightmare, I turned around and I saw
OL,8,Fmy girl standing there with Heidi.
OL,9,FHeidi had saved my daughter's life."
OL,11,FThe hearing, at Liverpool Town Hall,
OL,12,Faims to examine Axel Rudakubana's
OL,13,Fdealings with relevant agencies before
OL,14,Fhe carried out his violent attack on
OL,15,F29 July 2024.
OL,17,FAlice da Silva Aguiar, nine, Bebe
OL,18,FKing, six, and Elsie Dot Stancombe,
OL,19,Fseven, died in the incident, with the
OL,20,Fattacker attempting to murder 10
OL,21,Fothers.
