OL,6,FThe girl had hid in toilets with dance
OL,7,Fteacher Heidi Liddle as the attacker
OL,8,Flaunched a stabbing frenzy on innocent
OL,9,Fchildren attending a Taylor Swift
OL,10,Fthemed workshop at a dance studio on
OL,11,FHart Street in the town.
OL,13,FThey heard the screams of children on
OL,14,Fthe other side of the door and in
OL,15,Fheart-stopping moments, the killer
OL,16,Fbanging and rattling the handle trying
OL,17,Fto get inside their hiding place
OL,18,Fbefore police arrived, the public
OL,19,Finquiry into the attack heard.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
