OL,6,F"She had run towards the toilets
OL,7,Finstead of down the stairs with the
OL,8,Fother children," the mum said.
OL,10,F"Heidi had seen her and followed her
OL,11,Fand shielded the toilet door whilst he
OL,12,Ftried to get in.
OL,14,F"I owe everything to Heidi for having
OL,15,Fthe foresight to protect my daughter.
OL,17,F"She tells me she initially thought it
OL,18,Fwas a game of hide and seek.
