OL,6,F"I've no doubt in my mind, if Heidi
OL,7,Fhadn't have stayed in the building
OL,8,Fwith her, she wouldn't have made it
OL,9,Fout alive."
OL,11,FThe woman said that although both
OL,12,Fmother and daughter were physically
OL,13,Funscathed, they suffer daily from
OL,14,Fmental trauma.
OL,16,F"Since the incident, every day has
OL,17,Fbeen a day full of dysregulation,
OL,18,Fanxiety and depressive thoughts," the
OL,19,Fmother said.
