OL,6,FAnother mother told the hearing she
OL,7,Fwas parked up on the street on Hart
OL,8,FStreet outside the dance studio,
OL,9,Fhaving arrived early, when she saw her
OL,10,Fdaughter, referred to as C5, running
OL,11,Fpast and noticed she was covered in
OL,12,Fsomething.
OL,14,FShe said: "I heard screaming, I
OL,15,Fthought it was just children having
OL,16,Ffun.
OL,18,F"Then I saw our eldest running past
OL,19,Fme, she hadn't seen me so I shouted
OL,20,Fher back and that is when I realised
OL,21,Fher clothes were covered in something.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
