OL,6,F"At first I thought it must be paint,
OL,7,Fbut I soon realised it was blood.
OL,9,F"She heard me call her and ran back to
OL,10,Fme, telling me as she did 'Mum, I've
OL,11,Fbeen stabbed'.
OL,13,F"I didn't know what to do. Nothing
OL,14,Fcould have prepared me for the horror
OL,15,Fof seeing my child so horrifically
OL,16,Finjured."
