OL,6,FSpeaking of her daughter's mother
OL,7,Fcontinued: "She has described the
OL,8,Fimmense fear she felt in those
OL,9,Fmoments, how she didn't know what to
OL,10,Fdo or where to go.
OL,12,F"How she thought she would never see
OL,13,Fher family again. But she carried
OL,14,Fherself out of that building to safety.
OL,16,F"She saved her own life, and we are
OL,17,Fincredibly proud of her courage."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
