OL,6,FShe told the inquiry her daughter lost
OL,7,Fher entire blood volume at the scene
OL,8,Fand was rushed by air ambulance to
OL,9,FManchester Children's Hospital for
OL,10,Flife-saving surgery.
OL,12,FShe said: "She was minutes away from
OL,13,Fdeath and we thank god everyday for
OL,14,Fthe Midlands Air Ambulance crew, whose
OL,15,Fskill and dedication saved her life."
OL,17,FSpeaking of the impact on her
OL,18,Fdaughter, the mum continued: "She
OL,19,Fstruggles with constant guilt.
