OL,6,F"She asks what she could have done
OL,7,Fdifferently, whether she could have
OL,8,Fsaved the three little girls who lost
OL,9,Ftheir lives that day.
OL,11,F"It angers me that she carries this
OL,12,Fguilt. It is not her who has anything
OL,13,Fto feel guilty about. It was not her
OL,14,Fresponsibility to save those children."
OL,16,FThe inquiry was adjourned until next
OL,17,FMonday, when the families of the three
OL,18,Fgirls who died are due to give
OL,19,Fevidence.
